						<summary>

						<p>Pāṇḍya, Sundarapāṇḍya, 3rd year = 12th-13th Century.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record says that a gift of taxes on a <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> land was made by Avaninārāyaṇadēvaṉ for a festival on the day of Satayam (Śatabhishaj), the natal star of Nāyaṉār Chokkāṇḍār.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">Virudhunagar District Inscriptions</hi>, No. 131/2005.]</p>						

