<p>
<lb n="1"/>tiripuvaṉa cakkaravattikaḷ ciri cuntara
<lb n="2"/>pāṇṭiya tēvaṟku mūṉṟāvatu nāyaṉā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>r cokkāṇṭār Aruḷic ceyaṟpaṭi
<lb n="4"/>Avaṉinārāyaṇa tēvaṉṉē Iṭattu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vaḷi Uṭaiyār kuṟaṇmāṇīcuramu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭaiya nāyaṉār kōyilil Āḷuṭai
<lb n="7"/>ya piḷḷaiyārai nāyaṉār cokkā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṇṭār piṟanta nāḷ catayatti
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="31" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> nnāyaṉār kuṟaḷmāṇīcara
<lb n="11" break="no"/>muṭaiyār tēvatāṉak kaṭamai
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṉava viṉiyōkamum Ittiru
<lb n="13"/>nāḷukku Amutupaṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ttup paṭiyuḷ 
